    <nav>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/login">Login</a></li>
        <li><a href="/hikes">Hikes</a></li>

      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <article class="panel">
      <div class="text-wrapper left">
        <h2>Zion National Park</h2>
        <p>Utah is home to many national parks. Located near Springdale, Utah, this national park is home to many
          popular hikes. This includes
          the Narrows, and Angel's Landing (featured on the hero image).
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="button" id="button">Start tracking!</a>
      </div>
      <div class="image-wrapper">
        <img src="images/zion-600px.jpg" alt="Zion National Park" width="600" height="400">
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>

  <aside>
    <p><em>Hiking is fun!</em> There are lots of places to explore in Utah! Have fun tracking your hikes and looking for
      suggestions!</p>
  </aside>
  <footer>
    <p><strong>Website by Emma Bastian &copy; 2023</strong></p>
  </footer>

